description.plain:
Pierre David Guetta, better known simply as David Guetta, is a French DJ and producer. He first got a taste of the limelight with his 2009 album One Love which included the hit singles “When Love Takes Over”, “Gettin' Over You”, and “Sexy Bitch”, all three of which reached #1 in the UK and charted high internationally.

His 2011 album, Nothing but the Beat, continued this success, containing the hit singles “Where Them Girls At”, “Little Bad Girl”, “Without You”, “Titanium” and “Turn Me On”.

His sixth album Listen was released in 2014, and includes chart-toppers “Lovers on the Sun”, “Dangerous”, and “Hey Mama.” Most recently, in 2017, he released “2U” with Justin Bieber and “Dirty Sexy Money” in 2018 with Afrojack, Charli XCX and French Montana.

Pierre David Guetta, plus connu sous le nom de David Guetta, est un DJ français et producteur. Il prend d'abord avant-goût du milieu avec son album de 2009 “One Love” qui comprenait les hits “When Love Takes Over”, “Gettin' Over You”, et “Sexy Bitch”, les trois chansons sont arrivées premières au Royaume-uni et très dans les classements internationalement.

Son album de 2011 “Nothing but the Beat” l'a fait continué sur sa lancée, contenant les titres à succès “Where Them Girls At”, “Little Bad Girl”, “Without You”, “Titanium” et “Turn Me On”.

Son sixième album “Listen est sorti en 2014 et comprend notamment les titres "Lovers on the Sun”, “Dangerous” et “Hey Mama”. Plus récemment, en 2017, il a sorti “2U” avec Justin Bieber et “Dirty Sexy Money” en 2018 avec Afrojack, Charli XCX et French Montana.

songs.title: 2U

description.plain:
“2U” is a romantic ode to a woman who is worth the chase and time she demands.

On June 6, 2017, Justin teased the release of the song on Twitter. The promotion of the song was later followed by a series of post on social media, in which Victoria Secret models danced to it. After the release, those videos turned out to originate from Jerome Duran’s lip-sync music video. Furthermore, Guetta sent a few lucky fans the song’s full lyrics in advance of its premiere.

The song is the first official collaboration of the French DJ and the Canadian pop star, the latter of which has already been dominating the charts with DJ Khaled’s “I’m The One” and his remix of Luis Fonsi’s “Despacito.”

The single soared up to #1 on several charts, conforming a recent comment made by the chief of the label Justin is signed to, Def Jam Recordings' CEO Steve Bartels:

The remarkable thing about him right now is that he could be having the song of the summer without it being his own record

songs.title: Titanium

description.plain:
Sia and David Guetta’s massive track “Titanium” soared as the fourth single from Guetta’s Nothing but the Beat. Visceral, tall lyrics accompanying daring vocals and addictive production, “Titanium” acts as an anthem against the critics and the bullies, equating vicious criticisms to bullets.

The song was originally written for Mary J. Blige among other artists (including Katy Perry and Alicia Keys). Blige recorded the song but instead of releasing her version, Guetta used Sia’s original demo without her permission (complying with Katy’s suggestion). It soon became a hit, and Sia acknowledges the choice as a major benefactor in her songwriting career.

Chartwise, it was extremely successful, becoming a top ten hit in 17 countries and moving 3.8 million units in the United States alone.

description.plain:
“Hey Mama” is the fourth single from David Guetta’s sixth studio album, Listen. The beat is a pop/EDM collaboration with Afrojack. The song also features Nicki Minaj, who both sings and raps. Bebe Rexha sings the chorus. Meanwhile, the post-chorus includes a sample of Alan Lomax’s song “Rosie”.

Cover Art:



When the song was first released, the song had a different cover art, due to Bebe Rexha not originaly being credited.



Check out the official video:
